display.title: Google Gemini 3 Pro (Nano Banana 2)
display.modelDescription: A premium image model developed by Google, designed for clean, photorealistic enhancements and high-accuracy edits. Great for portraits, objects, and natural scenes where clarity, lighting control, and realism matter. Fast, reliable, and ideal for everyday creative use.

display.title: Google Gemini Flash 2.5 (Nano Banana)
display.modelDescription: Google’s lightweight and extremely fast image model optimized for speed-driven creativity. Perfect for quick edits, simple transformations, and fast turnarounds while still producing sharp, balanced results. Ideal for social content and rapid experimentation.

display.title: Seedream 4.5
display.modelDescription: Seedream is a Bytedance-built aesthetic image model known for dreamy lighting, smooth gradients, and magazine-like visual polish. Version 4.5 produces vibrant lifestyle imagery, cinematic outdoor scenes, stylized portraits, and soft artistic effects.

display.title: Seedream 4.0
display.modelDescription: An earlier but still beautiful version of Bytedance’s Seedream model, focusing on gentle realism, pastel tones, and atmospheric lighting. Great for travel-style photos, creative illustration, and soft artistic transformations.

display.title: FLUX.2 [dev]
display.modelDescription: A fully open and developer-focused model from Black Forest Labs, designed for anyone who wants deeper control over sampling, composition, and custom pipelines. Ideal for creators who want flexibility, experimentation, and advanced workflows with consistent high quality.

display.title: FLUX.1 Kontext [pro]
display.modelDescription: A professional-grade model from Black Forest Labs built for sharp detail, consistent anatomy, accurate lighting, and clean visual structure. Excellent for portraits, branding images, product photography, and polished commercial-quality artwork.

display.title: FLUX.1 Kontext [max]
display.modelDescription: The highest-performing model in the Kontext family—built for complex scenes, rich textures, dramatic lighting, and maximum realism. Ideal for cinematic artwork, large compositions, and high-impact creative visuals.

display.title: Z-Image-Turbo
display.modelDescription: Z-Image-Turbo is an ultra-fast image generation model developed by Tongyi-MAI, Alibaba’s advanced AI research division. Built using modern distillation techniques, it’s designed to deliver high-quality results at exceptional speed and low cost. Ideal for quick creative iterations, high-volume workflows, and fast drafts without sacrificing clarity.

display.title: Riverflow 2 Fast
display.modelDescription: Lightweight edition of Riverflow 2 for fast workflows and lower cost. Combines text-to-image generation with precise editing capabilities, supporting strong product accuracy across both workflows.

display.title: Riverflow 2 Standard
display.modelDescription: Balanced version of Riverflow 2 combining realistic output with reliable detail control and smooth integration of reference products for professional image creation. This unified model excels at both generation and editing workflows.

display.title: Riverflow 2 Max
display.modelDescription: Highest-quality version of Riverflow 2 focused on maximum detail, lighting control, and accuracy for demanding commercial work and premium product visuals. Delivers visuals that feel close to professionally staged photography.
